{
    "name": "Fyndylsnitch the Shadowking",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "A master of shadow magic, Fyndylsnitch delights in using his craft to warp reality. While it is suspected he holds great power, the Lord of Drearwood has never moved from his realm. For this reason, sages speculate he performs some sort of duty for a greater lord in First World."
        }
    ],
